name: Inspiration
desc: Encourage you and your allies within 30 meters. Gain 50 points in strength, agility, endurance and intelligence.

name: Intellect Conversion
desc: Every 10 points of int provides 1 point of magic atk power

name: Regen Bud
desc: Intial limit is 4. When skills are used to heal, 2 regen buds are consumed to throw out a Nourishing seed (1 sec cd, restores 40% of atk power as health) When skills are used to cause dmg, 2 regen buds are consumed to throw out a Wild seed (1 sec cd, deals 100% of atk power as dmg)

name: Defensive Blessing
desc: Encouragement now provides an additional 200 points of physical defense

name: Energy Surge
desc: Every 2% haste provides 1% energy recovery efficiency

name: Regeneration Bud
desc: When dealing dmg with basic attacks, 10% fixed chance to gain 1 regen bud

name: Healing Breath
desc:
When skills apply direct healing, there is a 20% chance to trigger a treatment link and every 2% luck increases trigger chance by 1%. 
 
Treatment Link: 
the healing chain bounces between friendly units, restoring 40% of atk power as health each time. Max number of bounces is 2.

name: Divine Ascension of the Flower Realm
desc: When wild seed or nourishing seed takes effect, gain 10% forest elemental bonus for 8 seconds

name: Dancing Seed
desc: When specialization skill triggers Lucky hit, the number of wild seeds launched next time is increased by 1. For every 5 nourishing seed thrown, next time is increased by 1.

name: Smite Spec
desc:
Enhanced Wild Bloom. Wild bloom,  Regeneration Pulse, Nature's Sanctuary apply Symbiotic Mark to friendly targets. Lasts for 6 seconds, all damage caused by self will be restored to Symbiotic Mark targets for 30% of the damage.

When there is no damage caused within five seconds, each basic attack will restore 12.6% max health to teammates

name: Natural Shield
desc: When Wildbloom heals, it also applies Nature's shield to the healed target. When attacked while Nature's shield is applied, heal by 10% of your attack power. CD 1 sec.

name: Thorns
desc: Wild Seed applies Thorns to the target when it its. Thorns targets receives +5% Forest Damage.

name: Shelter
desc: For 5 seconds after casting Infusion, the amount of damage Nature's Shield can receive is doubled.

name: Lucky Damage
desc: Lucky Hit Damage + 5%. Each 1% luck provides 1% lucky hit dmg.

name: Wild Blessing
desc: Wildbloom has 2 charges and costs -15% less energy.

name: Final Light Wheel
desc: When Wildbloom triggers Lucky Hit, cd of infusion will reduce by 3s.

name: Flower Language
desc: Replace ultimate with Flower Language ultimate skill.

name: Spread Thorns
desc: Thorns effect is spread to enemies within hit by feral seed

name: Pulse loopback
desc: Regeneration Pulse now deals dmg and returns after reaching maximum distance.

name: Gift of Energy
desc: Within 10m of an enemy killed, an energy orb will spawn and picking it up will grant 1 regen bud.

name: Untamed Seed Symbiosis
desc: When Symbiotic Marks >= 5, damage of Untamed Seed is increased by 100%

name: Pulse Echo
desc:
When infusion deals dmg, gain 1 stack of Pulse Echo. 

Effect:
Regeneration Pulse dmg +20%, last for 12 sec and can be stacked up to 5 times.

name: Breath of Symbiosis
desc: Symbiotic Mark healing +2%. Every 5% Mastery +1% healing.
